{"id": "art-114", "label": "Art. 114", "title": "Art. 114: Desemnarea tutorelui", "slug": "art-114", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_314376134\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1267\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_314376134\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 114:\nDesemnarea tutorelui </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_848554964\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1266\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_848554964\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)P&#259;rintele poate desemna, prin act unilateral sau\nprin conven&#355;ie, încheiate în form&#259; autentic&#259;, ori, dup&#259;\ncaz, prin testament, persoana care urmeaz&#259; a fi numit&#259; tutore al\ncopiilor s&#259;i.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1807310620\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1265\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1807310620\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Desemnarea f&#259;cut&#259; de p&#259;rintele care în\nmomentul mor&#355;ii era dec&#259;zut din drepturile p&#259;rinte&#351;ti este\nlipsit&#259; de efecte.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1826037098\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1264\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1826037098\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Desemnarea f&#259;cut&#259; în condi&#355;iile alin. (1)\npoate fi revocat&#259; oricând de c&#259;tre p&#259;rinte, chiar &#351;i\nprintr-un înscris sub semn&#259;tur&#259; privat&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_453081706\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1263\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_453081706\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)Înscrisul prin care se revoc&#259; persoana\ndesemnat&#259; pentru a fi numit&#259; tutore se va înscrie în registrul\nprev&#259;zut la art. 1.046 sau la art. 2.033, dup&#259; caz.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1700584538\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1262\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1700584538\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)Notarul public sau instan&#355;a de tutel&#259;,\ndup&#259; caz, are obliga&#355;ia s&#259; verifice la registrele prev&#259;zute\nla alin. (4) dac&#259; persoana desemnat&#259; pentru a fi tutore nu a fost\nrevocat&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_511750115\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1261\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_511750115\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(6)P&#259;rintele cu capacitate de exerci&#355;iu\ndeplin&#259;, care exercit&#259; autoritatea p&#259;rinteasc&#259; asupra\ncopilului s&#259;u minor sau care este tutorele copilului s&#259;u major cu\nprivire la care a fost instituit&#259; tutela special&#259;, poate s&#259;\nîncheie un contract de mandat de ocrotire cu privire la îngrijirea acestuia,\npentru situa&#355;ia în care mandantul decedeaz&#259; sau nu î&#351;i mai poate\nîndeplini sarcina tutelei. Dispozi&#355;iile prezentului alineat se aplic&#259;\n&#351;i rudelor de pân&#259; la gradul al doilea inclusiv care sunt tutori ai\nminorului sau ai majorului care beneficiaz&#259; de tutel&#259; special&#259;.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}